title: Design
text: Run usethis::use_data_raw("name_of_data_set") newly created file, write code produce desired data set. include following code data set saved pin. Remember change name_of_data_set match name data set. Push changes Main. Update modeldatatoo_board R/aaa-board.R include new data set. Run usethis::use_r("name_of_data_set") Populate following code. Changing name_of_data_set reflect name used earlier. Add information @details @source. Run devtools::document() Update NEWS.md Add data set _pkgdown.yml done!
code: library(pins)  board <- board_folder("data-raw/", versioned = FALSE)  board |>   pin_write(name_of_data_set, "name_of_data_set", type = "rds") #' name_of_data_set data set #' #' @return tibble #' #' @details #' #' # tibble print #' #' ```{r} #' data_name_of_data_set() #' ``` #' #' # glimpse() #' #' ```{r} #' tibble::glimpse(data_name_of_data_set()) #' ``` #' #' @examples #' \dontrun{ #' data_name_of_data_set() #' } #' @export data_name_of_data_set <- function() {   pins::pin_read(modeldatatoo_board, "name_of_data_set") }
